org.batfish.coordinator.resources

Class NetworkResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.coordinator.resources.NetworkResource

  • @Produces(value="application/json")
public class NetworkResource
extends Object
    The NetworkResource is a resource for servicing client API calls at container level.

    The NetworkResource provides information about a specified container, and provides the ability to delete a specified container for authenticated clients.

    The NetworkResource also provides the access entry for other subResources.
